text.tspan: Daily vs. Total confirmed COVID-19 cases
Shown is the 7-day rolling average of confirmed COVID-19 cases. The number of confirmed cases is lower than the
number of total cases. The main reason for this is limited testing.
Source: Johns Hopkins University CSSE COVID-19 Data – Last updated 20 May, 09:03 (London time)
